182
00:09:45,879 --> 00:09:46,840
Of course, I do.

183
00:09:50,039 --> 00:09:50,799
(Okay.)

184
00:09:51,559 --> 00:09:53,919
Then, I'll go through
fire and water for my boss.

185
00:09:56,080 --> 00:09:57,799
In a way as a boss to an employee.

186
00:10:00,159 --> 00:10:01,720
(I've actually learned to lie.)

187
00:10:09,120 --> 00:10:09,960
So,

188
00:10:10,919 --> 00:10:12,159
