189
00:10:12,200 --> 00:10:13,159
Of course not.

190
00:10:18,720 --> 00:10:19,600
(Liu Yali.)

191
00:10:21,600 --> 00:10:22,639
Let's work hard together

192
00:10:22,879 --> 00:10:23,879
for Flower Moon Night

193
00:10:25,399 --> 00:10:26,279
and your freedom.

194
00:10:36,320 --> 00:10:37,360
(Liu Yali.)

195
00:10:38,519 --> 00:10:41,120
You lied.

196
00:11:18,120 --> 00:11:18,919
Liu Yali.

197
00:11:22,240 --> 00:11:23,200
Actually,

198
00:11:25,240 --> 00:11:26,159
I like you.

